precis:
Enactment of SCHEDULE No. 894 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which
provides for the use of calcium disodium EDTA in canned snails and canned
sea snails, at a maximum level of 300 ppm, in order to inhibit
discolouration.
